{"title":"Redis之Hash","date":"2020-03-01T08:28:04.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 1, 2020","L":"03/01/2020","MM-DD":"03-01"},"thumbnail":"post/中间件/Redis/Redis之Hash/cover.png","link":"post/中间件/Redis/Redis之Hash","categories":["Redis","中间件"],"updated":"2020-03-02T01:39:27.882Z","content":"<h1 id=\"常用命令\">常用命令<a href=\"#常用命令\" title=\"常用命令\"></a></h1><p><strong>设置单个字段</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HSET key field value</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202221107.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>获取单个字段</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HGET key field value</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202218528.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>设置多个字段</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HMSET key field value [key field value]</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202609125.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>当字段不存在时设置</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HSETNX key field value</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301203048889.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>获取多个字段</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HMGET key field [field]</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202606103.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>获取所有字段名</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HKEYS key</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202902851.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>获取所有字段值</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HVALS key</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301203439739.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>获取所有字段名以及值</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HGETALL key</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202831068.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>获取字段数量</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HLEN key</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202924101.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>删除字段</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HDEL key field [field]</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202716424.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>判断字段是否存在</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HEXISTS key field</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301202757894.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>整数增加字段值</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HINCRBY key field increment</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301203155575.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<p><strong>浮点数增加字段值</strong></p>\n<ul><li>HINCRBYFLOAT key field increment</li>\n</ul><img src=\"/post/%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%B4%E4%BB%B6/Redis/Redis%E4%B9%8BHash/image-20200301203315754.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<h1 id=\"应用场景\">应用场景<a href=\"#应用场景\" title=\"应用场景\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"购物车\">购物车<a href=\"#购物车\" title=\"购物车\"></a></h2><ul><li>key：用户id</li>\n<li>fieldKey：商品编号</li>\n<li>fieldVal：商品数量</li>\n</ul>","prev":{"title":"Redis之Set","link":"post/中间件/Redis/Redis之Set"},"next":{"title":"Redis之String","link":"post/中间件/Redis/Redis之String"},"plink":"https://beginc.github.io/post/中间件/Redis/Redis之Hash/","toc":[{"id":"常用命令","title":"常用命令","index":"1"},{"id":"应用场景","title":"应用场景","index":"2","children":[{"id":"购物车","title":"购物车","index":"2.1"}]}]}